-- Denizbank Rejects Sharing Information With HSBC, Star Reports
-- B y   S e l c u k   G o k o l u k
-- 2012-01-02T06:36:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-02/denizbank-rejects-sharing-information-with-hsbc-star-reports.html
Denizbank AS (DENIZ) , the Turkish bank owned
by Dexia SA of Belgium, rejected sharing confidential
information with the Turkish unit of  HSBC Holdings Plc (HSBA) , Star
newspaper reported, without saying how it got the information.  Denizbank officials only agreed to share confidential
information with the visiting top managers of HSBC at a recent
meeting for a possible sale of Denizbank to HSBC, the Istanbul-
based newspaper said.  Link to Story   To contact the reporter on this story:
